channel.title: Port forwarding
channel.description:
[s]I'm having trouble port forwarding. I'm using the port 43594. I go on canyouseeme.org and it says, "Error: I could not see your service on 98.248.24.173 on port (43594) Reason: Connection timed out"
I also tried using uTorrent to port forward and that did not work either. I don't understand what I'm doing wrong. [/s]
Edit: Found out the problem. It was my phone service Vonage.. I disconnected it from my modem and people were able to connect to the server. Plus it made my internet go so much faster. ;)
